snippet.title: NALLI BIRYANI | Mutton Biryani Recipe Cooking in Village | Mutton Bone Marrow | Lamb Shanks Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, We cook the Nalli biryani recipe using fresh lamb shanks. We use Seeraga samba rice to make this traditional biryani recipe. The special of this mutton recipe is while eating biryani, and we taste a lot of bone marrow with the meat.

We enjoy the biryani at the evening! The taste is delicious!

snippet.title: J & V United by Love |Jisma Vimal Wedding| #lovestory #weddingvideo #southindianwedding
snippet.description:
J & V United by Love |Jisma Vimal Wedding| #lovestory #weddingvideo #southindianwedding 

" " United by Love " is a documentary focused on our journey from starting out as friends and aspiring actors, to falling in love and making it big through YouTube and finally getting married to each other. We come from southern part of India and we feel lucky to have a successful relationship even though our families follow different religions. We personally thank "Enchanteur", a brand centered around romance & love, joining hands with us in celebrating our love and making it special . Riding towards more adventure in our life and career, we pause for a moment and share these precious moments with you all. 

Love always, 

J& V

snippet.title: Jethalal से कैसे टूट गया Dining Table? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Express
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jethalal, Taarak, Bhide, Sodhi and others try to lift Doctor Haathi from the broken sofa. Jetha’s hand got slipped, and eventually, he hits the dining table. The glass table got scattered. Everyone gets scared at that time. Watch the full clip for hilarious moments. Stay tuned. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1778
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQA3TWG8mHLCRO_vFhMoYiV

Jethalal से कैसे टूट गया Dining Table? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Express

snippet.description:
Titanic submarine Missing: टलांटिक महासागर में 5 यात्रियों सहित गायब हुई टाइटन पनडुब्बी (Titanic submarine Missing) को लेकर कंपनी की तरफ से बताया गया है कि पनडुब्बी (Titanic submarine Missing) में सवार सभी 5 यात्रियों की मौत हो गई है. पनडुब्बी का मलबा टाइटेनिक जहाज (Titanic) के पास ही मिला है. दुनिया के सबसे बड़े और सबसे पॉपुलर जहाज रहे टाइटेनिक (Titanic Missing)को डूबे करीब 110 साल से भी ज्यादा का समय हो चुका है. इसका मलबा 1985 में ढूंढ लिया गया था.

snippet.title: Living like a Mermaid 🧜‍♀️ for a day!
snippet.description:
🧜‍♀️ Living Like a Mermaid for a Day! 🌊 Dive into an enchanting underwater adventure as we take on the ultimate mermaid challenge. Join us on this magical journey as we transform into mermaids and explore the wonders of the ocean! 🐠

In this captivating vlog, we'll show you how we prepared for our day as mermaids, including getting our mermaid tails, creating mesmerizing mermaid makeup looks, and styling our hair with shimmering shells and pearls. 🧜‍♀️✨

Once we're fully transformed, we'll take you along as we dive into the crystal-clear waters, swimming gracefully like real mermaids. Get ready to witness stunning underwater footage as we encounter colorful marine life, mystical coral reefs, and maybe even discover hidden treasures! 🐚🌈

But being a mermaid isn't just about swimming. We'll also indulge in delightful mermaid-themed snacks and drinks, perfecting our mermaid poses and dances, and enjoying the magical serenity of the ocean's embrace. It's a day filled with joy, wonder, and a touch of mermaid magic! 🌊🎉

So, if you've ever wondered what it's like to live as a mermaid, or simply want to embark on a whimsical adventure with us, don't miss this extraordinary experience. Dive into the deep blue with us and let your imagination swim free in this unforgettable mermaid journey! 🧜‍♀️💙

Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe to our channel to stay tuned for more incredible adventures. Hit that notification bell so you never miss a moment of our magical escapades! 🔔✨

আপোনালোকে ভৱাৰ দৰে মই ইমান বেয়া ছোৱালী নহয়। মই বিয়াত বহি সাংঘাতিক ভুল কৰিলোঁ। মই যে তৃতীয়গৰাকী পত্নী মই নাজানিছিলোঁ। কোঠাত বন্ধ কৰি মোক মাৰপিট কৰিছিল। কেমেৰাত সন্মুখত কিয় উচুপি উঠিল শ্যামন্তিকা শৰ্মা। 
#dy365 #shyamantikasharma #haridrahazarika #assam #sidhakotha
_______________________________

About Puthiya Thalaimurai TV

 Puthiya Thalaimurai TV (Tamil: புதிய தலைமுறை டிவி) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on August 24, 2011.Due to its independent editorial stance it became extremely popular in India and abroad within days of its launch and continues to remain so till date.The channel looks at issues through the eyes of the common man and serves as a platform that airs people's views.The editorial policy is built on strong ethics and fair reporting methods that does not favour or oppose any individual, ideology, group, government, organisation or sponsor.The channel’s primary aim is taking unbiased and accurate information to the socially conscious common man.
 
Besides giving live and current information the channel broadcasts news on sports,  business and international affairs. It also offers a wide array of week end programmes.
 
The channel is promoted by Chennai based New Gen Media Corporation.

Jhoom Episode 14 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Kadwani - Zara Noor Abbas - Digitally Presented by Spot-Less Skin With Ponds - 24th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Jhoom Digitally Presented by Spot-Less Skin With Ponds

A journey of JHOOM into the world of love, relationships, heartbreak, and sacrifice that centers around the lives of two souls who find love in a world of chaos and uncertainty that changes their lives forever. Aryaan is a young and handsome boy who holds a caring and possessive nature towards his friends. Despite having a traumatic past, Aryaan tries to smile through the worries of life and never steps back from helping his friends.

However, Aryaan's life takes an unexpected turn when he meets Maryam, a compassionate and kind-hearted woman who becomes a ray of sunshine in his life. As their relationship begin to flourish, Aryaan feels a change in himself and embraces the love that he had been deprived for so long.

Despite the significant age gap between them, Aryaan and Maryam's love for each other knows no bounds, and they embark on an unconventional journey together. Their love defies societal norms and expectations, challenging the prejudices and biases of those around them.

As their relationship progresses, their love is put to the ultimate test. Will they be able to overcome their challenges and sacrifices to stay together? Will their love stand the test of time and societal pressure? Is age just a number when it comes to love?

Written By: Hashim Nadeem
Directed By: Ali Faizan

Jhoom Digitally Presented by Spot-Less Skin With Ponds

A journey of JHOOM into the world of love, relationships, heartbreak, and sacrifice that centers around the lives of two souls who find love in a world of chaos and uncertainty that changes their lives forever. Aryaan is a young and handsome boy who holds a caring and possessive nature towards his friends. Despite having a traumatic past, Aryaan tries to smile through the worries of life and never steps back from helping his friends.

However, Aryaan's life takes an unexpected turn when he meets Maryam, a compassionate and kind-hearted woman who becomes a ray of sunshine in his life. As their relationship begin to flourish, Aryaan feels a change in himself and embraces the love that he had been deprived for so long.

Despite the significant age gap between them, Aryaan and Maryam's love for each other knows no bounds, and they embark on an unconventional journey together. Their love defies societal norms and expectations, challenging the prejudices and biases of those around them.

As their relationship progresses, their love is put to the ultimate test. Will they be able to overcome their challenges and sacrifices to stay together? Will their love stand the test of time and societal pressure? Is age just a number when it comes to love?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: മലപ്പുറം സ്കൂളിൽ മലയാളം പഠിപ്പിക്കുന്ന നേപ്പാളി പെൺകുട്ടി.
snippet.description:
#baseworld
#school
#teaching
#girl
#nepal
#poornimaray

 മലപ്പുറത്തുള്ള കോട്ടയ്ക്കൽ പറപ്പൂർ തെക്കേ കുളമ്പിലെ സ്കൂളിൽ ഒരു സിക്കിമിലെ പെൺകുട്ടി മലയാളം പഠിപ്പിക്കുന്ന വീഡിയോ ആണ് നമ്മൾ ഇതിൽ കാണിച്ചിരിക്കുന്നത്  സ്കൂളിൽ വന്നതിനുശേഷം ഒന്നാം ക്ലാസിൽ നിന്ന് ആറുമാസംകൊണ്ട് മലയാളവും ഇംഗ്ലീഷും അറബിയും പഠിച്ചെടുത്ത് മിടുക്കിയാണ് ഈ പൂർണിമ റായി  എന്നിവർക്ക് ഒരുപാട് ആരാധകരും അതുപോലെതന്നെ ടീച്ചേഴ്സിന്റെ സപ്പോർട്ട് കൂടി നല്ല രീതിയിൽ സ്കൂളിൽ പഠിച്ചു വരുന്നു. ഇവിടെ പഠിപ്പിക്കുന്നതിനായി സഫിയ ടീച്ചർ എന്ന് പറയുന്ന ടീച്ചറാണ് ഏറ്റവും അധികം കഷ്ടപ്പെട്ടിട്ടുള്ളത്

- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.

- Brawl Ball (3v3): It’s a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team’s safe and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.

Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers, Gadgets! and Gears! Level them up and collect unique skins!

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season!

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
Climb the local and regional leaderboards to prove you’re the greatest Brawler of them all!

CONSTANTLY EVOLVING
Look out for new Brawlers, skins, maps, special events and games modes in the future!

Tere Bin Episode 56 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 22nd June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: Kamala Harris Bursts into Laughter after PM Modi's this Comment at U.S. Congress | Watch
snippet.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi lauded Indian-origin US Vice President Kamala Harris while addressing the joint sitting of the US Congress and referred to "significant presence of millions of individuals in the United States who have ancestral ties to India." Modi, in a lighter vein, said "samosa caucus is now the flavour of the House" and hoped that more Indian foods are included in the future.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3806 | 24 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3806: Bagha Is Well Prepared
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide gives a sermon to Jethalal who was panicking about his meeting after Taarak was unable to clear his schedule. Jetha reaches the shop and is worried about the meeting. Bagha in the shop shows a presentation to Jetha about Gada Electronics and how the dealership will help the company. Jethalal is impressed by Bagha's presentation and English. Will he be successful in obtaining the Gada Electronics dealership? Watch the episode

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3806, 24 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: 1345: ⛴️ ടൈറ്റാനിക് കാണാൻ പോയ അന്തർവാഹിനി. ആഴത്തിൽ പോകുമ്പോൾ മനുഷ്യ ശരീരത്തിന് സംഭവിക്കുന്നത്?
snippet.description:
1345: ⛴️ ടൈറ്റാനിക് കാണാൻ പോയ അന്തർവാഹിനി.. The lost submarine.. എന്താണ് ഇത്രയധികം ആഴത്തിൽ പോകുമ്പോൾ മനുഷ്യ ശരീരത്തിന് സംഭവിക്കുന്നത്? What happens if you go too deep in the sea?

അറ്റ്ലാന്റിക് സമു​ദ്രത്തിനടിയിലെ ടൈറ്റാനിക്കിന്റെ അവശിഷ്ടങ്ങൾ കാണാനായി പോയ ടൂറിസ്റ്റ് അന്തർവാഹിനിക്കപ്പൽ കാണാതായത് നിങ്ങൾ അറിഞ്ഞതാണ്. ജൂൺ 18 ഞായറാഴ്ചയാണ് സംഭവം. കപ്പലിനായി ശക്തമായ തിരച്ചിൽ ഇപ്പോഴും തുടരുകയാണ്. പൈലറ്റുൾപ്പെടെ അഞ്ചുപേരെയാണ് കാണാതായത്. ശ​ബ്ദ​ത​രം​ഗ​ങ്ങ​ള്‍ ഉ​പ​യോ​ഗി​ച്ച് വെ​ള്ള​ത്തി​ന​ടി​യി​ലെ വ​സ്തു​ക്ക​ളെ ക​ണ്ടെ​ത്താ​ന്‍ ഉ​പ​യോ​ഗി​ക്കു​ന്ന സോ​ണാര്‍ യന്ത്രം ഉപയോഗിച്ചാണ് തിരച്ചിൽ.

അ​റ്റ്ലാ​ന്‍റി​ക് സ​മു​ദ്ര​ത്തി​ല്‍ 3,800 മീ​റ്റ​ര്‍ താ​ഴ്ച​യി​ലു​ള്ള ടൈ​റ്റാ​നി​ക്കി​ന്‍റെ അ​വ​ശി​ഷ്ട​ങ്ങ​ള്‍ കാ​ണാ​നാ​യി ഓ​ഷ്യ​ന്‍ ഗേ​റ്റ്സ് എ​ക്സി​പെ​ഡി​ഷ​ന്‍സ് സം​ഘ​ടി​പ്പി​ച്ച യാത്രയാണിത്. എന്താണ് ഇത്രയധികം ആഴത്തിൽ പോകുമ്പോൾ മനുഷ്യ ശരീരത്തിന് സംഭവിക്കുന്നത്. രക്ഷപെടാൻ സാധ്യതയുണ്ടോ? ഈ കാര്യങ്ങൾ അറിഞ്ഞിരിക്കുക. മറ്റുള്ളവർക്കായി ഷെയർ ചെയ്യുക.

#drdanishsalim #danishsalim #drdbetterlife #dybarism #titanic #submarine*****Dr.
 Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the “Best emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

Kismat Ne Jaane Ae Dil,
Ye Khel Kaise Khele,
Mann Ander Ander Rooye,
Ghum Sehta Rahe Akele…

Kisse Apna Haal Sunawa,
Kisse Apne Zakhm Dikhavaan,
Jo Beet Gaya Hai Mujhpe,
Main Jaanu Ya Dil Jaane…

Haaye Rabba…Haaye Rabba,
Koi Dard Na Jaane Mera Dard Na Jaane,
Haaye Rabba…Haaye Rabba,
Koi Dard Na Jaane Mera Dard Na Jaane,
Haaye Rabba…

Kacchi Thi Aas Ki Doori,
Ek Pal Mein Toot Gayi Hai,
Ye Apno Ki Khudgarzi,
Khushiyaan Meri Loot Gayi Hai…

iss Raah-E-Wafa Mein Paayi,
Har Modd Fakat Ruswayi,
Jo Manzil Ki Chahat Thi,
Rashte Mein Wo Chhut Gayi Hai…

Soona Mann Ka Aangan Hai,
Ye Kaisa Khali Pan Hai,
Mere Ander Hai Tanhaai,
Mere Bahar Hai Viraane…

Haaye Rabba…Haaye Rabba,
Koi Dard Na Jaane Mera Dard Na Jaane,
Haaye Rabba…Haaye Rabba,
Koi Dard Na Jaane Mera Dard Na Jaane,
Haaye Rabba…

Koi Puche Mere Dil Se,
Kaise Ye Zehar Piya Hai,
Marna Kisko Kaehte Hai,
Jitte Jee Ye Jaan Liya Hai…

Bedard Zamaane Se Main,
Koi Shikwa Karoon Kaise,
Humdard Jisse Samjha Tha,
Usne Hi To Dard Diya Hai…

Ye Soch Ke Dard Shoon Main,
Iss Dar Se Kuch Na Kahoon Main,
Ye Dil Ke Rishtey Pal Mein Ho Jaaye Na Begaane

Katra Katra Aakhon Se,
Kyun Behti Hai Majboori,
Jo Duayein Maangi Hai,
Wo Bhi Jaane Kab Hoomgi Poori…

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3805 | 23 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3805: Important Meeting Ki Tyaari
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is worried about his client meeting tomorrow because his pal Taarak will be unavailable. Taarak pays Jetha a visit after dinner and proposes he takes Bagha and Nattu Kaka because they are fluent in English and know a lot about the company. Jetha phones Bagha and requests an instant meeting, but Bagha is preoccupied with Bawri. As a result, Jetha and Taarak decide to pay a visit to Bagha and Nattu Kaka. Taarak informs Bagha and Nattu Kaka about their managing meeting. Nattu Kaka believes it would be strange if Jetha, as the owner, remained mute while his employers dealt with the clients. So, what happens next? Will Taarak devise a new strategy?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3805, 23 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 725 & 726 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 725 & 726 | Recap

Ekam and Harleen get confused seeing Sartaj and Nehmat driving off somewhere else while they return home to find a shocker. Ekam receives Sartaj's letter and learns that he has made Ekam the owner of all the properties. How will everyone react?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: Challengers - Official Trailer - Warner Bros. UK & Ireland
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for #ChallengersMovie starring Zendaya, Josh O’Connor, and Mike Faist. Directed by Luca Guadagnino, only in cinemas September 15.

From visionary filmmaker Luca Guadagnino, Challengers stars Zendaya as Tashi Duncan, a former tennis prodigy turned coach and a force of nature who makes no apologies for her game on and off the court. Married to a champion on a losing streak (Mike Faist – West Side Story), Tashi’s strategy for her husband’s redemption takes a surprising turn when he must face off against the washed-up Patrick (Josh O’Connor – The Crown) – his former best friend and Tashi’s former boyfriend. As their pasts and presents collide, and tensions run high, Tashi must ask herself, what will it cost to win.

*About* 
------------

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 37: Kaashvi Ka Pehla Jurm
-------------------------------------------------
Baalveer looks for his mother in Udaka Lok but is unable to locate her. Shaashmaag learns from surveillance that Baalveer has violated the boundaries of Udaka Lok. He summons Baalveer and tries to have him arrested along with one of his henchmen. Baalveer poses as a regular lad from Dharti Lok who stumbled onto this mysterious location. Shaashmaag arrests Baalveer and brings him to Maha Mahim Uttan because she doesn't believe him. Aageel is busy hatching her cunning scheme to control Kaashvi through Maha Jadoo. Will Kaashvi commit human sins while under Aageel's sway?

Show Name – Baalveer S3
Star Cast – Dev Joshi, Aditi Sanwal, Ada Khan, Behzaad Khan, Aditya Ranvijay
Episodes No - 37, 23 June 2023
Produced By - Vipul D Shah

#baalveer3  #बालवीर3 #sab

The new season of Baalveer follows the journey of the 24-year-old superhero who draws strength from his mother. The season revolves around his journey from Veer to Baalveer, regaining his identity and the world he belongs to with the help of partner Kaashvi.

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

*About* 
------------

           Yeh kahani hai ek sidhi sadhi, padhi likhi, pyaari si, Pratigya aur ameer, bigdel, badtameez Krishna ki. Pratigya ki parvarish hui ek sadharan par acche parivaar mein jaha padhai aur sanskaron ko diya gaya bohot mahatva. Wahi doosri taraf apne parivaar mein Krishna ne dekhi zulm aur paise ki taakat. Isi taakat ke dum par zabardasti ki Krishna ne Pratigya se shaadi. 
           Pratigya ke sasural aur maayke mein hai zameen aur aasmaan ka faasla. Krishna ki haveli mein prem aur aadar ka hai akaal. Aise mein kya hoga Pratigya ka haal? Waqt ke sath Pratigya- Krishna ne kiya hazaaron mushkilon ka saamna aur door hua dono ke beech ka faasla. Ek anchaha rishta ban gaya sacche pyaar ki misaal.

snippet.title: मा० श्री ⁦#शरद_पवार जी के बिहार आगमन पर राजद राष्ट्रीय अ. श्री लालू यादव जी से उनके आवास पर भेंट की
snippet.description: Rashtriya Janta Dal locates itself in the collective aspirations of people and communities striving to carve out a society based on the premises of social justice and secularism. Since its inception Rashtriya Janta Dal is relentlessly working as the voice of the socially and economically downtrodden sections of the society. The RJD believes in working on and propagating socialist politics and towrds this end the party has been developing solidarity network of landless labourers, peasants and farmers other weaker groups as well as progressive people from other sections of society. Drawing inspiration from Gandhian values as well as following in the great tradition of the socialist leaders, RJD strongly stands against communalism in any form. The party believes that the right of peaceful and democratic dissent including Satyagraha/ non-violent resistance is a fundamental right of the people.

snippet.title: നിങ്ങൾക്ക് അറിയാത്ത നീതുസിന്റെ  ജീവിതം | @Neethuzzz | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
തന്മയത്വമുള്ള അഭിനയവും കണ്ടന്റും കൊണ്ട് യുട്യൂബിൽ അഞ്ചര ലക്ഷം ആരാധകരെ സ്വന്തമാക്കാന്‍ ഈ വൈറൽ വീട്ടമ്മയ്ക്ക് സാധിച്ചു. ടിക് ടോകിലൂടെ തുടങ്ങിയ അഭിനയമാണ് നീതുവിനെ ഇന്ന് മറ്റാരുടെയും മുന്നിൽ കൈനീട്ടാതെ സ്വന്തമായി സമ്പാദിക്കാൻ കഴിയുന്ന നിലയിൽ കൊണ്ടെത്തിച്ചത്. നമ്മളെ ഒക്കെ ചിരിപ്പിച്ചു സന്തോഷിപ്പിക്കുന്ന നീതുവിനും പറയാനുണ്ട് കൊറേ വേദനപ്പിക്കുന്ന അനുഭവങ്ങൾ . Tiktok ലൂടെയാണ് നീതു ആദ്യമായി വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യാൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്. പിന്നീട് youtube ലും instagram ലും വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യതാണ് നീതു താരം അവൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്.  തന്റെ കുട്ടികാലത്തും പിന്നീടും അനുഭവിച്ച വെല്ലുവിളികളും ആണ് നീതു ഇന്നത്തെ വിഡിയോയിൽ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നത് .

With her exceptional acting skills and captivating personality, Neethu gained a dedicated fan base of over five lakh on YouTube. Her viral videos brought her recognition and allowed her to make a name for herself without relying on others. She has shared both joyful and painful experiences that resonate with all of us. It all started with her videos on TikTok, and later she expanded to YouTube and Instagram. In her current video, she reflects on the challenges she faced in her childhood and throughout her journey.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

localized.title: നിങ്ങൾക്ക് അറിയാത്ത നീതുസിന്റെ  ജീവിതം | @Neethuzzz | Josh Talks Malayalam
localized.description:
തന്മയത്വമുള്ള അഭിനയവും കണ്ടന്റും കൊണ്ട് യുട്യൂബിൽ അഞ്ചര ലക്ഷം ആരാധകരെ സ്വന്തമാക്കാന്‍ ഈ വൈറൽ വീട്ടമ്മയ്ക്ക് സാധിച്ചു. ടിക് ടോകിലൂടെ തുടങ്ങിയ അഭിനയമാണ് നീതുവിനെ ഇന്ന് മറ്റാരുടെയും മുന്നിൽ കൈനീട്ടാതെ സ്വന്തമായി സമ്പാദിക്കാൻ കഴിയുന്ന നിലയിൽ കൊണ്ടെത്തിച്ചത്. നമ്മളെ ഒക്കെ ചിരിപ്പിച്ചു സന്തോഷിപ്പിക്കുന്ന നീതുവിനും പറയാനുണ്ട് കൊറേ വേദനപ്പിക്കുന്ന അനുഭവങ്ങൾ . Tiktok ലൂടെയാണ് നീതു ആദ്യമായി വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യാൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്. പിന്നീട് youtube ലും instagram ലും വീഡിയോസ് ചെയ്യതാണ് നീതു താരം അവൻ തുടങ്ങിയത്.  തന്റെ കുട്ടികാലത്തും പിന്നീടും അനുഭവിച്ച വെല്ലുവിളികളും ആണ് നീതു ഇന്നത്തെ വിഡിയോയിൽ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നത് .

With her exceptional acting skills and captivating personality, Neethu gained a dedicated fan base of over five lakh on YouTube. Her viral videos brought her recognition and allowed her to make a name for herself without relying on others. She has shared both joyful and painful experiences that resonate with all of us. It all started with her videos on TikTok, and later she expanded to YouTube and Instagram. In her current video, she reflects on the challenges she faced in her childhood and throughout her journey.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

snippet.title: Ranbir Kapoor Ramayan vs Adipurush Movie | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Ranbir Kapoor Ramayan vs Adipurush Movie Reaction By Deeksha Sharma. Adipurush Prabhas Film Dialogue Controversy has united everyone & led to downfall in Adipurush Box Office Collection. But Bollywood is ready with another version of Ramayan Featuring Ranbir Kapoor & Alia Bhatt directed by Nitesh Tiwari. Will Om Raut Adipurush mistakes lead to ban on Ranbir Kapoor Ramayan? Kriti Sanon as Sita Mata will push Alia Bhatt to the limit & Ranbir Kapoor vs Prabhas will there be justice to Lord Ram in Bollywood? Do leave your Public Review in the Comments Section.
